### 1. Login
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### 2. Verify 2FA (Replace code with current TOTP)
# Use Secret: K6SPSURZ6YV6
POST http://localhost:8000/api/2fa/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "123456"
}

### 3. Swap Currency (Requires 2FA)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/swap
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 10000,
    "from_currency": "NGN",
    "to_currency": "CNY"
}

### 4. Get Ledger History
GET http://localhost:8000/api/ledger/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Webhook (Mock Settlement)
# Signature is computed as HMAC-SHA256(payload, 'mock-secret')
POST http://localhost:8000/api/webhooks/settlement
X-Signature: {{signature}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider_reference": "REF-12345",
    "amount": 5000,
    "wallet_id": 1,
    "user_id": 1
}
